CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. 10 reads: "AKA Debs - Preparing to make their bow Penn-Sheraton Hotel, May 18, under the auspices of Alpha Kappa Alpha sorority, are these charming young ladies. Pictured are Roberta Durham, Frances Pace, Connie Powell, Marva Jones, and Gayle Sands..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of 1957 Alpha Kappa Alpha Debutantes including Frances Pace standing on left, gathered in interior
